Text: I can't type right now, I'm doin' my Happy Dance! Awww thanks! You rock! It's ok if you picture me doing the dance PeeWee Herman does in the bar with the big white platform shoes to Tequila by Tito Fuentes. I don't mind! :-D
My daughter just asked if I could find All You've Got. I can't. It was made in 2006.
Good movie choice. excellent quality...thank you.
